1 NEW FOLLOWER = 1 MEAL for children in need.✨ Stella the polar bear wants you to know that you can make a difference for children in need today! ⁠
⁠
For the entire month of September, we’re donating 1 meal for every new follower.🍲 Tag a friend who you think would like to help! ⁠
⁠
At cuddle+kind, we believe every child deserves to have enough food to thrive. That’s why our fair trade, hand-knit dolls give 10 meals to children in need. Coming together as a community can change lives, and we’re so lucky to have supporters like you, fighting to end childhood hunger with us.💗⁠
⁠
{📸: @anastazja.and.theo } #1newfollowequalsonemeal #handmadewithlove #1dollequals10meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

node.text:
Hooray!✨ Claire the koala in her fresh mint romper is NOW AVAILABLE in limited quantities! Find her on our website now, link in bio.⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Be the first to see this gorgeous new colour in person, it truly is unique and so soothing for littles. Our artisans always amaze us with their skill and true passion for handcrafting dolls to bring your little ones comfort. Claire is hand-knit with natural Peruvian cotton yarn, and we think you’ll fall in love with how exceptionally soft she is in real life. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Swipe to see Claire in both her beautiful romper colours - will you be collecting both?⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Claire is available in both our regular 20” and our little 13” sizes, and is a permanent addition to our collection!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Your purchase of Claire the koala is extra-meaningful because she is artisan made, fair trade, and provides 10 meals to children in need.⁠⁠
⁠⁠
{📸: @ravenvasquezcreative } #koala #newrelease #handmadewithlove #1dollequals10meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

node.text:
GIVEAWAY CLOSED // Congratulations to @madeline_eric_baby and @tilnjosh , you’ve each won a Claire the koala doll! 

NEW KOALA GIVEAWAY!✨To celebrate the launch of Claire the koala in her fresh, modern mint romper, we are giving her to one lucky winner and a friend! ⁠
⁠
Mint Claire will be available at our online shop on Thursday, September 9th at 9:00am EDT. Each cuddle+kind doll is artisan made, fair trade and helps feed children in need. To enter, just follow the steps below:⁠
⁠
Follow @cuddleandkind 💕⁠
Like this photo 👍⁠
Tag a friend ☺ (Both you and our friend must be following @cuddleandkind to win.) For an extra chance to win, enter on our Facebook page too!⁠
⁠
The winner and their friend will each receive a hand-knit, cuddle+kind Claire the koala doll! You may enter as many times as you wish, as long as you tag different people each time. Contest closes at midnight EDT tonight (September 8th). We will announce the winner on Thursday, September 9th at 8:30am EDT. Good luck! Every cuddle+kind doll gives 10 meals to children in need. You can shop the collection now, link in bio.⁠
⁠
{📸: @ravenvasquezcreative } #koala #newrelease #handmadewithlove #1dollequals10meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

✨KOALA SNEAK PEEK!✨ We are soooo excited to share a surprise look at Claire the koala in a new, gorgeous mint romper! We’ve been working with our artisans in Peru to create the perfect soft, modern shade and couldn’t be more proud of the result. ⁠
⁠
We love how fresh this colour looks with the whimsical hand-knit details of her romper. Our artisans spend a substantial amount of time handcrafting the delicate eyelet ruffle, and her darling crocheted cuffs. ⁠
⁠
Claire will be a permanent addition to our collection along with her original orchid romper: so you and your little one can choose your favourite, or collect them both! ⁠
⁠
She will be available to purchase on September 9th at 9:00am EDT. Make sure to follow along this week for more of her handcrafted details. We hope you and your little ones will love Claire’s fresh, new romper as much as we do!⁠
⁠
{📸: @ravenvasquezcreative } #koala #newrelease #handmadewithlove #1dollequals10meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

Get FREE SHIPPING, today only!🎊 Happy birthday to Lucy the lamb!🎂⁠
⁠
Today, you’ll receive free shipping on orders that include Lucy the lamb in her berry or pastel romper with code LUCY. Hurry, offer ends 11:59 pm PST tonight!⁠
⁠
Lucy is a gentle, loving little lamb with such darling handcrafted details, like the special textured stitch on her head that little ones love to touch and feel. And we think her substantial pink bow is the sweetest finishing detail! Our artisans create Lucy stitch by beautiful stitch with passion and love, and we’re so proud to have her in our collection. ⁠
⁠
Your purchase of Lucy the lamb today will provide 10 meals to children in need. Shop now at the link in our bio.✨ Happy birthday, Lucy!⁠
⁠
{📸: @ravenvasquezcreative } #handmadewithlove #1dollequals10meals #cuddleandkind #onemillionmeals #fairtrade

1 new follower = 1 meal!🎉 For the entire month of September, we will be donating 1 meal for every new follower on Instagram! ⁠
⁠
We’re a family of five on a mission to help feed children through our stylish collection of hand-knit dolls.✨ Every doll is handmade by artisans in Peru and gives meals to children around the world through our respected giving partners: World Food Program USA, Children’s Hunger Fund, and Breakfast Club of Canada.⁠
⁠
Every child deserves to have enough food to eat to survive and thrive. Tag a friend who would like to help!💞⁠
